"Change Set:		7976Traits-nice.235Traits-nice.235:remove uncessary sends of #valuesbecause (aDictionary values do:) is same as (aDictionary do:)except when aDictionary is modified in the do loop."!!TraitDescription methodsFor: 'private' stamp: 'nice 10/19/2009 20:58'!linesOfCode	"An approximate measure of lines of code.	Includes comments, but excludes blank lines."	| lines |	lines := self methodDict inject: 0 into: [:sum :each | sum + each linesOfCode]. 	self isMeta 		ifTrue: [^ lines]		ifFalse: [^ lines + self class linesOfCode]! !